short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Draw labeled annotations over image attachments in Trello™ cards. Easy and secure. Watch a demo at http://husky.io

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enhances your Trello™ cards and allows you to add labeled annotations to image attachments. Annotated images are saved in your Trello™ card and can be shared with others (event without the need of this extension!). Easy and secure. Watch a demo at http://husky.io
